<div class="container my-5">
    <h3 class="text-center urbanist-bold text-blue mb-5">Why Choose FitSync?</h3>

    <div class="row text-center">
        
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <i class="fas fa-robot fa-3x mb-3"></i>
            <h4 class="urbanist-bold text-blue">AI-Powered Workout Planning</h4>
            <p class="urbanist-medium">
                Get a custom routine generated specifically for your body, goals, and history. No more generic plans.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <i class="fas fa-hand-pointer fa-3x mb-3"></i>
            <h4 class="urbanist-bold text-blue">Easy, Flexible Tracking</h4>
            <p class="urbanist-medium">
                Track your progress effortlessly. Manually enter workouts or integrate with a common fitness API like **Fitbit**.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-line fa-3x mb-3"></i>
            <h4 class="urbanist-bold text-blue">Visualize Your Progress</h4>
            <p class="urbanist-medium">
                View detailed performance **graphs** and **statistics**—including completion rate and progress over time—to stay motivated.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <hr class="my-5">
    
    <div class="text-center mt-5">
        <h4 class="urbanist-bold text-blue">Already have an account?</h4>
        <a asp-page="/LogIn" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-signin mt-2">Log In Now</a>
    </div>

</div>

